  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6636600/" class="title-link">这本书的内容基本都是抄的 而且不客观</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6636600"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/40043350/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u40043350-7.jpg"></a>
