  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7370037/" class="title-link">战争就是这么回事儿</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7370037"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3095014/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3095014-13.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3095014/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">enenn</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-02-06"
      class="main-meta">2015-02-06 13:08:41</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7370037_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  袁老师也算是用心良苦，用说书的方式调侃历史，不就是想勾起大伙儿对读史的好奇心嘛。问题是战争这回事儿没法逗闷子，光靠历史的边角料当包袱，再时不时拿意大利人开涮，大家是没法记住这段残酷战争史的。心智未育的00后们，看了就看了，图个乐呵，可别当真。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
